name: CGInterpolationQuality
desc: Levels of interpolation quality for rendering an image.

items.name: case low
items.desc: A low level of interpolation quality. This setting may speed up image rendering.

items.name: case medium
items.desc: A medium level of interpolation quality. This setting is slower than the low setting but faster than the high setting.

items.name: case high
items.desc: A high level of interpolation quality. This setting may slow down image rendering.
